casebody.data:
State of KANSAS, plaintiff,
v.
State of NEBRASKA and State of Colorado. No. 126, Original. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 13, 2014. Report of the Special Master received and ordered filed. Exceptions to the Report, with supporting briefs, may be filed within 45 days. Replies, if any, with supporting briefs, may be filed within 30 days. Sur-replies, if any, with supporting briefs, may be filed within 30 days.
